      "name": "AndyVPN Panel Backend",
      "description": "VPN service management panel at iii.andyvpnc.com running PHP 5.4.45 on nginx. Handles user registration, login, subscription management, and VPN server assignment. Exposed .env and .git/HEAD files.",
